media:group.media:title: Sonic Frontiers Showdown Official Trailer
media:group.media:description:
It's almost time. Explore the Starfall Islands, gather the Chaos Emeralds, and get ready for the showdown of a lifetime in Sonic Frontiers.

Sonic Frontiers releases on November 8th, 2022 on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X and S, Nintendo Switch, and Steam!
